  // Utility function to calculate the mean of an array
  calculateMean = (arr) => {
    const sum = arr.reduce((acc, val) => acc + val, 0);
    return sum / arr.length;
  };

  // Utility function to calculate the median of an array
  calculateMedian = (arr) => {
    const sortedArr = arr.slice().sort((a, b) => a - b);
    const middleIndex = Math.floor(sortedArr.length / 2);

    if (sortedArr.length % 2 === 0) {
      return (sortedArr[middleIndex - 1] + sortedArr[middleIndex]) / 2;
    } else {
      return sortedArr[middleIndex];
    }
  };

  // Utility function to calculate the mode of an array
  calculateMode = (arr) => {
    const frequencyMap = {};
    let maxFrequency = 0;
    let modes = [];

    arr.forEach((value) => {
      frequencyMap[value] = (frequencyMap[value] || 0) + 1;
      if (frequencyMap[value] > maxFrequency) {
        maxFrequency = frequencyMap[value];
        modes = [value];
      } else if (frequencyMap[value] === maxFrequency) {
        modes.push(value);
      }
    });

    return modes;
  };

  // Utility function to calculate the class-wise statistics of Flavanoids
  calculateClassStats = () => {
    const { dataset } = this.state;
    const classStats = {};

    dataset.forEach((dataObj) => {
      const { Alcohol, Flavanoids } = dataObj;

      if (!classStats[Alcohol]) {
        classStats[Alcohol] = {
          Flavanoids: [Flavanoids],
        };
      } else {
        classStats[Alcohol].Flavanoids.push(Flavanoids);
      }
    });

    Object.keys(classStats).forEach((alcoholClass) => {
      const flavanoidsArray = classStats[alcoholClass].Flavanoids;

      classStats[alcoholClass].Flavanoids = {
        Mean: this.calculateMean(flavanoidsArray),
        Median: this.calculateMedian(flavanoidsArray),
        Mode: this.calculateMode(flavanoidsArray),
      };
    });

    return classStats;
  };

  render() {
    const classStats = this.calculateClassStats();

    return (
      <div>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Measure</th>
              {Object.keys(classStats).map((alcoholClass) => (
                <th key={alcoholClass}>Class {alcoholClass}</th>
              ))}
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Flavanoids Mean</td>
              {Object.keys(classStats).map((alcoholClass) => (
                <td key={alcoholClass}>
                  {classStats[alcoholClass].Flavanoids.Mean.toFixed(2)}
</td>
))}
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Flavanoids Median</td>
{Object.keys(classStats).map((alcoholClass) => (
<td key={alcoholClass}>
{classStats[alcoholClass].Flavanoids.Median.toFixed(2)}
</td>
))}
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Flavanoids Mode</td>
{Object.keys(classStats).map((alcoholClass) => (
<td key={alcoholClass}>
{classStats[alcoholClass].Flavanoids.Mode.join(', ')}
</td>
))}
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
);
